Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当月光照射黑暗的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说在宇宙飞舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.64,0:00:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展开决斗之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.41,0:00:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡的呼声远远的传开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.82,0:00:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶为此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.73,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换取持续戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.90,0:00:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为命运而不知所措之\N叹息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.31,0:00:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因无法抹去的记忆\N而为爱颤抖着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.25,0:01:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当月光照亮黑夜之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.09,0:01:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说促使得宇宙舞动着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.13,0:01:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的坠天使们啊\N美丽的飞翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的决斗展开时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.84,0:01:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遥远的地方呼喊着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.28,0:01:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三话迷宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂小弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，一大早的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.59,0:02:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊\N我会有很长一段时间不去上学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你跟老师说一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗拜托啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.53,0:02:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原因?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找绫香啊，我的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有为了维护地球的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.27,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说明的话话就长了\N我要挂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早啊，红英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们干嘛呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.42,0:02:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是"你们"呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做布丽姬妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是亚娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.66,0:02:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚娘、布丽姬妲、雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.37,0:02:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么来着?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜，城琉菜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换洗的衣服准备好了\N英司少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.98,0:03:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不需要我们帮您换衣服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说不必了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.69,0:03:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是被人家脱光光\N谁受得了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.06,0:03:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出不来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.46,0:03:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感应器到底怎么啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在磨蹭什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这叫做缩头乌龟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸，你知道怎么用吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，真会找麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上那新的衣服过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.64,0:04:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要乖乖的等着哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也得再洗一次澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别偷看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.32,0:04:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死都不会看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，等会见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，为什么不是自动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.94,0:05:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好慢哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空腹正是最好的调味料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会议差不多要开始了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.51,0:05:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算做任何的说明啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有圣日耳曼城的背景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.05,0:06:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连那个机器人是由谁、\N怎么制造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些全都是机密是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.19,0:06:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们地球战骑队所要求的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.20,0:06:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有对抗外星异种的所有权限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有需要\N政府各局的支援的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会主动提出请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是要我们别插手管啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.64,0:06:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为军队是养来干什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.35,0:06:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从地球由单一政府统驭\N这十多年来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.65,0:06:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类过着\N完全没有纷争的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.93,0:06:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球联合政府军、EFA的战力\N的确是在水准之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.86,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在实战经验方面\N却存在着问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.33,0:06:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想说我们因为过得太舒服\N变得毫无用处了是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太无礼了，说话当心点\N雷文先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现实上在昨天的战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.95,0:07:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EFA对于外星异种\N无法有效的歼灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现阶段来说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.59,0:07:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将一切的战斗\N交给神机超重神才是最上策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信也已经实际证明过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.10,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢在此大放厥词...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.58,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想找你姊姊吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为了这个目的\N留在这座城堡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个字迹绝对是绫香的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.42,0:07:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫香一定还在这座城堡的某处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那么担心你姊姊的安危吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.09,0:07:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你也有亲人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.20,0:07:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是突然间断了音讯\N你不会担心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯... 我会怎样呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么你会吧你，你啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.51,0:08:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这座城堡的事情\N我比你清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我帮你吧，可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有见过绫香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.52,0:08:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我听说过她是在\N训练期间在西塔失踪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.09,0:08:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,训练...\N是操控神机超重神的训练吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是用模拟器的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.56,0:08:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，那个就是\N绫香失去踪影的西塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实要是没有桑德曼的许可\N是不可以进去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.10,0:08:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸， 我们不会迷路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.87,0:08:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的\N我从小就住在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会迷路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从小?你家人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?是琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别，别这样...不是啦别误会啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.62,0:09:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫"死也不会偷看"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.79,0:09:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看在你是刚到城堡的份上\N想对你好一点的说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了...误会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么误会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.07,0:09:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个变态!色鬼、偷窥狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点琉菜，听我说嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是误会一场啦喔琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊，还真会到处乱跌耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.55,0:09:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢"跌倒"吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛跟来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很在意嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.53,0:10:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶G战影的\N搞不好就是绫香吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也来这里半年多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是有很多事情都搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼也不肯说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.37,0:10:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你，不是很早就住进来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被桑德曼找来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.21,0:10:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我只是在一般的学校上学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.95,0:10:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来的时候\N是绫香已经失踪之后的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么，什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊，快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷，您在哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.78,0:10:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我滚出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛，又跌倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都别动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，看来很不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办，斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙了，桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.21,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷跟斗牙少爷\N还有琉菜小姐都不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南栋地下三楼A区，动作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.23,0:12:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人进去了\N所以触发了机器人动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是斗牙他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上叫他们过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.57,0:12:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，真会挑时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听爱娜说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.72,0:12:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙小时候\N有个特训设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.86,0:12:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙在婴儿时期就失去了父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着被桑德曼所收留了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.73,0:12:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就一直在这座城堡里受训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.17,0:12:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了因应外星异种来袭之时\N所设定的训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到昨天驾驶\N神机超重神出击之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没踏出过城堡一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既没有上学、也没有朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.78,0:13:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到彻底的战士训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.48,0:13:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然真的有耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.58,0:13:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外也有其他的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从小就一直在做这种事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也觉得他是个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到真的是个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险 斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过别动的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.98,0:13:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊，我是在帮你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.99,0:13:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的战斗能力太低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便乱动的话\N只会碍手碍脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.20,0:14:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请立即出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在斗牙他们过来之前\N可别大意哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.61,0:14:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷、琉菜小姐\N请快点过来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸...\N加侬的弹装交换系统是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.53,0:15:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜!快逃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.81,0:15:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G重钻机，报告受损情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上部装甲破损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.58,0:15:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右侧飞弹装置无法使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合神结构方面正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.99,0:15:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后部机座人员到达后\N立刻进入合神状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜，打开舱门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心一点，琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是，要好好的操控哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.31,0:15:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，这样就没有问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.41,0:15:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜，等您等了好久喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战骑的诸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.08,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动合神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工学型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.64,0:17:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.71,0:17:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我军已经进入备战状态了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您下令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.28,0:17:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有必要的话我们会提出请求的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还未到那种阶段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，让我们瞧瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的战斗实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,献丑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们地球战骑队的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.53,0:17:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半径一公里范围内\N的对人搜寻没有反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居民已完成避难措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.21,0:18:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神机超重神重力子反应\N安定指数99%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.74,0:18:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距临界点为止9988点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.48,0:18:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种的攻击力以及防御力\N应该都一起进化了才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不可大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.76,0:18:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.13,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它进化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种正在放电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力系统传达机能降下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.03,0:18:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子反应安定指数\N下降到64%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离临界点为止7421点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电流啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员，使用各自负责的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对外星异种进行扫射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个浑蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧，超重飞弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全弹发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干得好，英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.98,0:19:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下子\N不准说我是碍手碍脚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.05,0:19:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离临界点为止\N只剩下2022点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.69,0:19:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙，快使用超重剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.59,0:19:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.69,0:19:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑身亮现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工学终结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那..那是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.79,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然能在地面使用出\N威力这么强大的武器...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考核通过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.85,0:20:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果，西塔还是没去成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.32,0:21:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫香真的还在这座城堡里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.76,0:21:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.82,0:21:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走着瞧吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.72,0:21:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会找出绫香\N跟这座城堡说掰掰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人真有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.03,0:21:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.04,0:21:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫香，等着我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.72,0:21:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着在烈阳热气下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.40,0:21:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈现形形色色的摆动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.44,0:21:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知该为何这般\N心头思绪纷乱不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.28,0:22:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就这么视而不见\N朝向明日飞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为无法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.86,0:22:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才说出了这么不客气的话语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.23,0:22:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤单一人地强出头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.03,0:22:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换来的只有误解\N矛盾与迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.01,0:22:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于那牵系着悲伤的羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.14,0:22:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让微笑的双眸中渗出了泪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.72,0:22:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想将这暖意传送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.52,0:22:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便紧握着手一直不愿放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.42,0:22:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让这祈祷得以传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.60,0:22:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷，救命啊\N有...有鬼出现了啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.17,0:22:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耍白痴啊，裘伊露你是在作梦...\N哇!那是...那白影是什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.57,0:22:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下...回播出"塔中的小公主"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.51,0:23:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下...周让我们继续照料\N各位的和平吧!